## Github fetch


![github.fetch](github.fetch.png)

Updates your local repository but does not change
the code you are working on

(1) click on fetch origin


 <P>&nbsp

## Github pull


![github.pull](github.pull.png)


Updates your local repository  and merges new code
with old work

 (1) click on pull origin button


